Query: Get the top 10 orders that have the highest total price.
Structure:
Select all orders from Orders
Order by Total_Amount in descending order
Limit to 10 results
Code: SELECT * FROM Orders ORDER BY Total_Amount DESC LIMIT 10;

Query: Get the top 5 products that have the highest average rating.
Structure:
Select Products.Product_Id and Products.Name from Products
Join Reviews on Products.Product_Id = Reviews.Product_Id
Group by Products.Product_Id
Order by AVG(Reviews.Rating) descending
Limit 5
Code:
SELECT Products.Product_Id, Products.Name
FROM Products
JOIN Reviews ON Products.Product_Id = Reviews.Product_Id
GROUP BY Products.Product_Id
ORDER BY AVG(Reviews.Rating) DESC
LIMIT 5;

Query: Get the top 5 users who spend the most money.
Structure:
Get the Full_Name, Email, and Total_Amount from Users
Join Users and Orders on User_Id
Group by User_Id
Order by Total_Amount descending
Limit 5
Code:
SELECT Users.Full_Name, Users.Email, SUM(Orders.Total_Amount) AS Total_Amount
FROM Users
JOIN Orders ON Users.User_Id = Orders.User_Id
GROUP BY Users.User_Id
ORDER BY Total_Amount DESC
LIMIT 5;
